CHECK:COMPARISON_TO_NULL: Comparison to NULL could be written "!chan->local"
#74: FILE: drivers/dma/dmaengine.c:358:
+		if (chan->local == NULL)

Comparisons to NULL in the form (foo == NULL) or (foo != NULL)
are better written as (!foo) and (foo).

